00:04:12.537 --> 00:04:14.552
the spring constant,

00:04:14.552 --> 00:04:17.834
times the spring constant,
times how much you've

00:04:17.834 --> 00:04:20.572
compressed the spring squared.

00:04:20.572 --> 00:04:23.780
So, the potential energy
increases as a sqaure

00:04:23.780 --> 00:04:25.938
