that getting converted into?

00:06:01.370 --> 00:06:04.215
Well, it's gonna get
converted into, into heat,

00:06:04.215 --> 00:06:05.496
due to the friction.

00:06:05.496 --> 00:06:07.357
So that's where, ya know, energy cannot be

00:06:07.357 --> 00:06:09.943
cannot be created out of thin
air or lost into thin air,

00:06:09.943 --> 00:06:12.609
